<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَم بِظَاهِرٍ مِّنَ الْقَوْلِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> تُسَمُّونَهُمْ شُرَكَاءَ فِي ظَاهِرِ القَوْلِ، مِنْ غَيْرِ أَنْ يَكُونَ لَهُمْ حَقِيقَةٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُكُلُهَا}</span> ... ثَمَرُهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عُقْبَى}</span> ... عَاقِبَةُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الأَحْزَابِ}</span> ... المُتَحَزِّبِينَ، المُتَجَمِّعِينَ عَلَى الكُفْرِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
